% Role & Scope
  Handler for `pal list` command. Displays all saved scripts.

% Requirements
  1) Interface `ListHandlerOptions`: context (LocalContext)
  2) Default export: `listHandler(options: ListHandlerOptions): Promise<void>`
  3) Get all commands via scriptManager.getAllCommands()
  4) If empty: write "No scripts found."
  5) Otherwise: write count, then for each command:
     - Name on one line
     - Description indented on next line

